<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SeTech AI — 세부특기사항 생성기</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mammoth/1.6.0/mammoth.browser.min.js"></script>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');
  :root {
    --bg:#0f1117;--surface:#1a1d27;--surface2:#222536;--border:#2e3247;
    --accent:#5b7fff;--accent2:#7c9fff;--green:#4ade80;--yellow:#fbbf24;
    --red:#f87171;--orange:#fb923c;--text:#e8eaf0;--text2:#9099b5;--text3:#5a6380;
    --radius:12px;--radius-sm:8px;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
  body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'Noto Sans KR','Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;min-height:100vh;}

  /* 헤더 */
  header{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 32px;height:56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;position:sticky;top:0;background:var(--bg);z-index:100;}
  .logo{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:-0.3px;}
  .logo span{color:var(--accent);}
  .header-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
  .api-badge{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);cursor:pointer;transition:border-color 0.2s;}
  .api-badge:hover{border-color:var(--accent);}
  .api-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--text3);}
  .api-dot.connected{background:var(--green);}
  .prompt-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;}
  .prompt-btn:hover{border-color:var(--yellow);color:var(--yellow);}

  /* 레이아웃 */
  .container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 24px;}

  /* 스텝 */
  .steps{display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:36px;}
  .step{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text3);transition:all 0.2s;cursor:pointer;}
  .step.active{background:var(--surface2);color:var(--accent2);}
  .step.done{color:var(--green);}
  .step-num{width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid currentColor;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;flex-shrink:0;}
  .step.done .step-num{background:var(--green);border-color:var(--green);color:#000;}
  .step-line{flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border);min-width:20px;max-width:40px;}

  /* 패널 */
  .panel{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:24px;margin-bottom:20px;}
  .panel-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.8px;margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
  .badge{font-size:10px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--surface2);color:var(--accent);text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;}
  .badge-yellow{color:var(--yellow);}
  .badge-red{color:var(--red);}

  /* 업로드 */
  .upload-zone{border:1.5px dashed var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);padding:28px 20px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;position:relative;}
  .upload-zone:hover,.upload-zone.dragover{border-color:var(--accent);background:rgba(91,127,255,0.04);}
  .upload-zone input[type="file"]{position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:0;cursor:pointer;width:100%;height:100%;}
  .upload-icon{font-size:28px;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .upload-label{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);}
  .upload-label strong{color:var(--accent2);}
  .upload-hint{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:4px;}
  .file-list{margin-top:12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;}
  .file-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:8px 12px;background:var(--surface2);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:12px;}
  .file-icon{font-size:16px;flex-shrink:0;}
  .file-name{flex:1;color:var(--text);overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap;}
  .file-size{color:var(--text3);flex-shrink:0;}
  .file-remove{color:var(--text3);cursor:pointer;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;transition:all 0.15s;flex-shrink:0;}
  .file-remove:hover{color:var(--red);background:rgba(248,113,113,0.1);}
  .file-status{font-size:10px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:10px;flex-shrink:0;}
  .file-status.ok{background:rgba(74,222,128,0.12);color:var(--green);}

  /* 폼 */
  textarea,select,input[type="text"],input[type="password"]{width:100%;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);color:var(--text);font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;font-size:13px;padding:10px 14px;outline:none;transition:border-color 0.2s;}
  textarea{resize:vertical;line-height:1.7;}
  textarea:focus,select:focus,input:focus{border-color:var(--accent);}
  textarea::placeholder,input::placeholder{color:var(--text3);}
  label.field-label{display:block;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.6px;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .char-counter{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);text-align:right;margin-top:4px;}

  /* 그리드 */
  .grid-2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;}
  @media(max-width:700px){.grid-2{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}

  /* 버튼 */
  .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:7px;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:13px;font-weight:500;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:all 0.2s;}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;}
  .btn-primary:hover{background:var(--accent2);transform:translateY(-1px);}
  .btn-primary:disabled{opacity:0.4;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none;}
  .btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--text2);border:1px solid var(--border);}
  .btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent2);}
  .btn-ghost:disabled{opacity:0.4;cursor:not-allowed;}
  .btn-green{background:var(--green);color:#000;font-weight:600;}
  .btn-green:hover{opacity:0.9;transform:translateY(-1px);}
  .btn-green:disabled{opacity:0.4;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none;}
  .btn-yellow{background:var(--yellow);color:#000;font-weight:600;}
  .btn-yellow:hover{opacity:0.9;}
  .btn-sm{padding:6px 14px;font-size:12px;}

  /* 결과 테이블 */
  .result-table-wrap{overflow-x:auto;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);border:1px solid var(--border);}
  table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12px;}
  thead th{background:var(--surface2);padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;font-weight:500;color:var(--text2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);white-space:nowrap;}
  tbody tr{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  tbody tr:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  tbody tr:hover{background:rgba(91,127,255,0.04);}
  tbody td{padding:10px 14px;vertical-align:top;}
  .td-setech{min-width:400px;max-width:500px;}
  .setech-edit{width:100%;background:transparent;border:1px solid transparent;border-radius:4px;color:var(--text);font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;padding:4px 6px;resize:none;outline:none;transition:border-color 0.2s;min-height:80px;}
  .setech-edit:focus{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--surface2);}
  .byte-count{font-size:11px;margin-top:3px;text-align:right;}
  .byte-ok{color:var(--green);}
  .byte-warn{color:var(--yellow);}
  .byte-over{color:var(--red);}
  .status-dot{display:inline-block;width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;margin-right:4px;}
  .dot-done{background:var(--green);}
  .dot-loading{background:var(--yellow);animation:pulse 1s infinite;}
  .dot-error{background:var(--red);}
  @keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1;}50%{opacity:0.3;}}

  /* 진행 바 */
  .progress-wrap{background:var(--surface2);border-radius:4px;height:4px;overflow:hidden;margin:12px 0;}
  .progress-bar{height:100%;background:var(--accent);border-radius:4px;transition:width 0.4s;}

  /* 액션 바 */
  .action-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 0;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .action-bar-left{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;}
  .action-bar-right{display:flex;gap:10px;}

  /* 알림 */
  .alert{padding:10px 14px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:12px;margin-bottom:12px;line-height:1.6;}
  .alert-info{background:rgba(91,127,255,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(91,127,255,0.2);color:var(--accent2);}
  .alert-warn{background:rgba(251,191,36,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.2);color:var(--yellow);}
  .alert-error{background:rgba(248,113,113,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.2);color:var(--red);}

  /* 모달 */
  .modal-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.75);backdrop-filter:blur(4px);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:200;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity 0.2s;}
  .modal-overlay.open{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto;}
  .modal{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:28px;width:460px;max-width:95vw;max-height:90vh;overflow-y:auto;transform:translateY(10px);transition:transform 0.2s;}
  .modal-overlay.open .modal{transform:translateY(0);}
  .modal-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .modal-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:20px;line-height:1.6;}
  .modal-actions{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:16px;}

  /* 프롬프트 편집기 전용 */
  .prompt-modal .modal{width:820px;}
  .prompt-tabs{display:flex;gap:4px;margin-bottom:16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding-bottom:0;}
  .prompt-tab{padding:8px 16px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text3);cursor:pointer;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-1px;transition:all 0.2s;}
  .prompt-tab.active{color:var(--accent2);border-bottom-color:var(--accent);}
  .prompt-tab:hover{color:var(--text2);}
  .prompt-section{display:none;}
  .prompt-section.active{display:block;}
  .prompt-tag{display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;font-family:'Inter',monospace;margin:2px;cursor:pointer;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--accent2);transition:all 0.15s;}
  .prompt-tag:hover{border-color:var(--accent);background:rgba(91,127,255,0.1);}
  .section-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.6;}

  /* 금지어/주의어 태그 */
  .word-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;margin-top:8px;}
  .word-tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:12px;font-size:12px;}
  .word-tag-forbid{background:rgba(248,113,113,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.25);color:var(--red);}
  .word-tag-caution{background:rgba(251,191,36,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.25);color:var(--yellow);}
  .word-tag-remove{cursor:pointer;opacity:0.6;font-size:10px;}
  .word-tag-remove:hover{opacity:1;}
  .word-input-row{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:10px;}
  .word-input-row input{flex:1;padding:8px 12px;}

  /* 구분선 */
  hr{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:20px 0;}

  @media(max-width:600px){header{padding:0 16px;}.container{padding:20px 16px;}.steps{overflow-x:auto;padding-bottom:4px;}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- API 키 모달 -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="apiModal">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-title">🔑 Gemini API 키 설정</div>
    <div class="modal-desc">Google AI Studio에서 발급한 API 키를 입력하세요.<br>키는 이 브라우저에만 저장되며 외부로 전송되지 않습니다.</div>
    <label class="field-label">API Key</label>
    <input type="password" id="apiKeyInput" placeholder="AIza..."/>
    <div class="modal-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="closeModal('apiModal')">취소</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="saveApiKey()">저장</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 프롬프트 편집기 모달 -->
<div class="modal-overlay prompt-modal" id="promptModal">
  <div class="modal" style="width:820px;">
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:4px;">
      <div class="modal-title">⚙️ 프롬프트 편집기</div>
      <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" onclick="resetPrompts()" style="font-size:11px;">↺ 기본값 초기화</button>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-desc">각 섹션을 독립적으로 수정하세요. 변수는 클릭하면 커서 위치에 삽입됩니다.</div>

    <!-- 탭 -->
    <div class="prompt-tabs">
      <div class="prompt-tab active" onclick="switchTab('role')">① 역할 지시</div>
      <div class="prompt-tab" onclick="switchTab('rules')">② 작성 규칙 ★</div>
      <div class="prompt-tab" onclick="switchTab('output')">③ 출력 형식</div>
      <div class="prompt-tab" onclick="switchTab('words')">④ 금지어 / 주의어</div>
    </div>

    <!-- 변수 태그 -->
    <div style="margin-bottom:12px;">
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:6px;">사용 가능한 변수 (클릭하면 삽입)</div>
      <div>
        <span class="prompt-tag" onclick="insertVar('{{학생이름}}')">{{학생이름}}</span>
        <span class="prompt-tag" onclick="insertVar('{{반번호}}')">{{반번호}}</span>
        <span class="prompt-tag" onclick="insertVar('{{과목명}}')">{{과목명}}</span>
        <span class="prompt-tag" onclick="insertVar('{{최대바이트}}')">{{최대바이트}}</span>
        <span class="prompt-tag" onclick="insertVar('{{성취기준}}')">{{성취기준}}</span>
        <span class="prompt-tag" onclick="insertVar('{{모범예시}}')">{{모범예시}}</span>
        <span class="prompt-tag" onclick="insertVar('{{과제내용}}')">{{과제내용}}</span>
        <span class="prompt-tag" onclick="insertVar('{{금지어목록}}')">{{금지어목록}}</span>
        <span class="prompt-tag" onclick="insertVar('{{주의어목록}}')">{{주의어목록}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 섹션: 역할 지시 -->
    <div class="prompt-section active" id="tab-role">
      <div class="section-desc">AI의 기본 역할과 전문성을 설정합니다. 거의 수정할 필요 없습니다.</div>
      <textarea id="prompt-role" rows="6"></textarea>
    </div>

    <!-- 섹션: 작성 규칙 -->
    <div class="prompt-section" id="tab-rules">
      <div class="section-desc">★ 가장 자주 수정하는 섹션입니다. 세특 작성 규칙과 스타일 지침을 설정하세요.</div>
      <textarea id="prompt-rules" rows="14"></textarea>
    </div>

    <!-- 섹션: 출력 형식 -->
    <div class="prompt-section" id="tab-output">
      <div class="section-desc">AI의 응답 형식을 지정합니다. 불필요한 설명이 포함될 때 수정하세요.</div>
      <textarea id="prompt-output" rows="6"></textarea>
    </div>

    <!-- 섹션: 금지어/주의어 -->
    <div class="prompt-section" id="tab-words">
      <div class="section-desc">금지어는 절대 사용 불가, 주의어는 되도록 피하되 맥락에 따라 허용됩니다.</div>

      <label class="field-label" style="margin-bottom:10px;">🔴 금지어 <span style="font-weight:300;text-transform:none;">(생활기록부 기재 금지)</span></label>
      <div class="word-tags" id="forbidTags"></div>
      <div class="word-input-row">
        <input type="text" id="forbidInput" placeholder="금지어 입력 후 Enter" onkeydown="addWord(event,'forbid')"/>
        <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" onclick="addWordBtn('forbid')">추가</button>
      </div>

      <hr/>

      <label class="field-label" style="margin-bottom:10px;">🟡 주의어 <span style="font-weight:300;text-transform:none;">(되도록 사용 자제)</span></label>
      <div class="word-tags" id="cautionTags"></div>
      <div class="word-input-row">
        <input type="text" id="cautionInput" placeholder="주의어 입력 후 Enter" onkeydown="addWord(event,'caution')"/>
        <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" onclick="addWordBtn('caution')">추가</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="modal-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="closeModal('promptModal')">취소</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="savePrompts()">💾 저장</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 헤더 -->
<header>
  <div class="logo">Se<span>Tech</span> AI</div>
  <div class="header-right">
    <div class="prompt-btn" onclick="openPromptModal()">⚙️ 프롬프트 편집</div>
    <div class="api-badge" onclick="openModal('apiModal')">
      <div class="api-dot" id="apiDot"></div>
      <span id="apiStatus">API 키 미설정</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <!-- 스텝 인디케이터 -->
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step active" id="step1-ind" onclick="goStep(1)"><div class="step-num">1</div>준비</div>
    <div class="step-line"></div>
    <div class="step" id="step2-ind" onclick="goStep(2)"><div class="step-num">2</div>과제물</div>
    <div class="step-line"></div>
    <div class="step" id="step3-ind" onclick="goStep(3)"><div class="step-num">3</div>생성</div>
    <div class="step-line"></div>
    <div class="step" id="step4-ind" onclick="goStep(4)"><div class="step-num">4</div>검토 &amp; 다운로드</div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 1 -->
  <div id="step1">
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-title">📋 NEIS 양식 파일 <span class="badge">필수</span></div>
        <div class="upload-zone" id="neisZone" ondragover="onDrag(event,'neisZone')" ondragleave="offDrag('neisZone')" ondrop="onDrop(event,'neis')">
          <input type="file" accept=".xlsx,.xls" multiple onchange="handleFile(event,'neis')">
          <div class="upload-icon">📊</div>
          <div class="upload-label"><strong>클릭 또는 드래그</strong>하여 업로드</div>
          <div class="upload-hint">학급별 xlsx 파일 (여러 개 동시 선택 가능)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="file-list" id="neis-files"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-title">📚 성취기준 <span class="badge">권장</span></div>
        <div class="upload-zone" id="achZone" ondragover="onDrag(event,'achZone')" ondragleave="offDrag('achZone')" ondrop="onDrop(event,'ach')">
          <input type="file" accept=".pdf,.txt,.docx" onchange="handleFile(event,'ach')">
          <div class="upload-icon">🎯</div>
          <div class="upload-label"><strong>클릭 또는 드래그</strong>하여 업로드</div>
          <div class="upload-hint">2022 교육과정 성취기준 PDF/TXT</div>
        </div>
        <div class="file-list" id="ach-files"></div>
        <div style="margin-top:12px;">
          <label class="field-label">또는 직접 입력</label>
          <textarea id="achText" rows="5" placeholder="[9종교01-01] 종교의 본질과 특성을 이해하고...&#10;[9종교01-02] 다양한 종교의 세계관을 비교하여..."></textarea>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-title">✍️ 모범 예시 문장 <span class="badge">스타일 학습용</span></div>
      <div class="alert alert-info">이전에 작성한 세특 문장 3~5개를 붙여넣으세요. AI가 선생님의 문체·어휘·문장 구조를 학습합니다.</div>
      <textarea id="exampleText" rows="8" placeholder="예시1) 종교의 본질에 관한 탐구 활동에서 다양한 종교적 세계관을 비교·분석하며 자신만의 종교관을 정립하는 과정을 성실히 수행함.&#10;&#10;예시2) 생명윤리 단원에서 안락사 문제에 대해 다양한 종교적 입장을 조사하고 자신의 견해를 근거 있게 제시함." oninput="updateCounter('exampleText','exampleCounter')"></textarea>
